sequenceDiagram
    participant DSPCtrl as DSP Pipeline Controller
    participant DSPUI as DSP UI / Pipeline SDK
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC/HTTP2<br/>Optional TLS + mTLS
    participant DB as MySQL / MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP<br/>Optional SSL

    Note over DSPCtrl,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Metadata Recording

    DSPCtrl->>MLMD: PutExecution(execution, artifacts, events, contexts)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 | 8080/TCP | Optional TLS
    activate MLMD
    Note right of MLMD: ConnectMetadataStore()<br/>(new DB connection per RPC)
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE metadata<br/>MySQL protocol | 3306/TCP | Optional SSL<br/>Auth: Username/password
    DB-->>MLMD: Query result
    MLMD-->>DSPCtrl: PutExecutionResponse
    deactivate MLMD

    DSPCtrl->>MLMD: PutArtifacts(artifacts)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 | 8080/TCP
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE artifacts
    DB-->>MLMD: Query result
    MLMD-->>DSPCtrl: PutArtifactsResponse
    deactivate MLMD

    DSPCtrl->>MLMD: PutEvents(events)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 | 8080/TCP
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT events (artifact-execution relationships)
    DB-->>MLMD: Query result
    MLMD-->>DSPCtrl: PutEventsResponse
    deactivate MLMD

    Note over DSPUI,DB: Flow 2: Lineage Query

    DSPUI->>MLMD: GetLineageSubgraph(request)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 | 8080/TCP | Optional TLS
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT lineage data<br/>MySQL protocol | 3306/TCP | Optional SSL<br/>Auth: Username/password
    DB-->>MLMD: Lineage graph data
    MLMD-->>DSPUI: GetLineageSubgraphResponse<br/>(artifacts, executions, contexts, events)
    deactivate MLMD

    DSPUI->>MLMD: GetArtifactsByContext(context_id)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 | 8080/TCP
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT artifacts WHERE context_id
    DB-->>MLMD: Artifact records
    MLMD-->>DSPUI: GetArtifactsByContextResponse
    deactivate MLMD
